Our top priorities are customer service and safety.  You can trust Proline Electric in your home or place of business. Need an electrician call Proline Electric Ltd.! We are your Electrician!

Why People Choose Proline Electric! Your Friendly Electrician!

We only hire the best Electricians; 
Our Electricians are Drug Tested, Background Checked and Licensed.  

Upfront Pricing: 
We will show you the exact price and get your approval before starting your electrical work.  In addition, we stand by our quoted price.  You'll never pay more.
